>
  <h1>Aircraft Squad Building</h1>
  <p class="text-lg text-[#8a96b0]">Guide in progress — pending verification. Last reviewed: July 2026.</p>

  <QuickSummary>
    <p>We don't have a verified hero build for Aircraft squads yet. The full guide is coming once our hero-type verification pass is complete — see <a href="/squad-building" class="text-[#f59e0b] hover:underline">Squad Building</a> for the general principles (mono-type, positioning, Main Squad First) that are already verified.</p>
  </QuickSummary>

  <h2>What We Can Say So Far</h2>
  <ul class="text-sm space-y-1">
    <li>Per the type triangle on our <a href="/stats" class="text-[#f59e0b] hover:underline">Stats</a> page, Aircraft counters Tank. This cycle direction is reverse-engineered by the community, not from official patch notes — treat it as directionally useful, not settled.</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-[#8a96b0]">No hero-specific advice appears here until it clears our two-source verification bar. Check back after the hero-type pass lands.</p>

  <div class="mt-6">
    <a href="/squad-building" class="text-[#f59e0b] hover:underline">← Back to Squad Building Principles</a>
